                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Amazon.com:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">Barry Sears looks at why Americans still have dietary problems in spite of following the advice of experts. Challenging the current recommendations for a high carbohydrate diet, Sears looks into man's history as well as the diets athletes succeed best on, to build a new dietary picture.  Anyone looking for better health through an improved relationship to what they eat should put this book on their list.</span>
              
