                    <span>I found this book in a thrift store for $2, after hearing about it from an ex girlfriend.  It takes a while to figure it out, but after like 2 weeks I mastered it.   People who have problems understanding this, just are't trying hard enough.  Anyway , I lost 20 pounds, and I'm at my ideal weight now.  All this with barely working out.   I have more energy throughout the day, and more importantly, a lot more confidence.  There is sacrifice involved, but once you get to where I am, you really can't see living any other way.  Highly recommended.</span>
                  
